Web Site: http://www.nirsoft.net

This utility lists all NTFS alternate streams found in the current
directory. You can also scan other folders by using -f and -d
parameters:

-f [Folder Path]

Specified the folder that you wish to scan.

-d [Subfolders Depth]

Specified the depth of subfolders to scan. (0 = none, 1 = first level of subfolders, and so on)

Example:

AltStreamDump.exe -f "c:\myfolder" -d 3






